<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="favicon.png">
  <title>Melonlorrd's Blog</title>

  <style>
    /* =========================================================
       Layout tokens
       ========================================================= */
    :root {
      --max-width: 720px;
      --side-padding: 1.25rem;
      --radius: 6px;
      --font-body: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
      :root {
        /* Base – warm, airy, soft contrast */
        --bg: #faf8f3;           /* warm morning white */
        --bg-alt: #f1ede3;       /* soft sand */
        --surface: #e8e2d6;      /* light warm gray */

        /* Text */
        --fg: #3a3f46;           /* deep slate */
        --fg-muted: #6b7280;     /* cool gray */
        --heading: #2d6cdf;      /* fresh sky blue */

        /* Accents */
        --link: #1f75d8;         /* ocean blue */
        --link-hover: #0f9d8a;   /* breezy teal */

        /* UI */
        --border: #ddd6c8;
        --code-bg: #f1ede3;
        --inline-code-bg: #e8e2d6;
      }
    }

    @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
      :root {
        /* Base – Ayu Mirage / Ocean Winter inspired */
        --bg: #1f2430;           /* deep blue night */
        --bg-alt: #232936;       /* soft navy */
        --surface: #2a3142;      /* muted steel */

        /* Text */
        --fg: #d6deeb;           /* cool light */
        --fg-muted: #9aa5b1;     /* desaturated blue-gray */
        --heading: #73d0ff;      /* icy cyan */

        /* Accents */
        --link: #5ccfe6;         /* ocean cyan */
        --link-hover: #ffd580;   /* warm sunset contrast */

        /* UI */
        --border: #3a4154;
        --code-bg: #232936;
        --inline-code-bg: #2a3142;
      }
    }

    /* =========================================================
       Base styles
       ========================================================= */
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--fg);
      font-family: var(--font-body);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    main {
      max-width: var(--max-width);
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 0 var(--side-padding);
    }

    h1, h2 {
      color: var(--heading);
      line-height: 1.3;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2rem);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.5rem);
      margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    }

    p {
      margin: 0.5rem 0 1rem;
      color: var(--fg-muted);
    }

    a {
      color: var(--link);
      text-decoration: none;
      border-bottom: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: color 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease;
    }

    a:hover {
      color: var(--link-hover);
      border-color: var(--link-hover);
    }

    /* =========================================================
       Posts list
       ========================================================= */
    ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: baseline;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.75rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    li:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
    }

    time {
      flex-shrink: 0;
      min-width: 5.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--fg-muted);
    }

    /* =========================================================
       Responsive tweaks
       ========================================================= */
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      main {
        margin: 2rem auto;
      }

      li {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.25rem;
      }

      time {
        min-width: unset;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <main>
    <a class="back" href="index.html">Melonlorrd's Blog</a>

    <section>
      <h1>About</h1>
      <p>Hello! I'm Mahaprasad, passionate about Infrastructure and Systems Engineering. I currently work at AceCloud as a Cloud-DevOps Engineer. Outside work, I enjoy Music and Sketching.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/mprasadme" target="_blank">LinkedIn</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://github.com/melonlorrd" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h1>Posts</h1>
      <ul>
        {{ range . }}
        <li>
          <time>{{ .Date.Format "2006-01-02" }}</time>
          <a href="{{ .Slug }}.html">{{ .Title }}</a>
        </li>
        {{ end }}
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
